cs.NI, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.IT, cs.MM

The paper discusses the use of massive MIMO for 5G-connected UAVs, which involves network infrastructure and communication technologies. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). Additionally, the paper also touches upon the control and coordination of UAVs, which falls under the category of cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also discusses the need for reliable and safe communication, which can be categorized under cs.SY (Systems and Control). The use of advanced communication technologies such as 5G and beyond also falls under the category of cs.IT (Information Theory). Finally, the paper mentions the use of live video streaming, which can be categorized under cs.MM (Multimedia).
